      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Every Data Source Should Be an MCP Server (Including Your Operating System)</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">MCP is quietly becoming the standard for how agents talk to everything. This changes how agents interact with organizational intelligence.</p>
